Mabelle Gilman Corey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mabelle_Gilman_Corey 0 Mabelle Gilman Corey (December 4, 1874 – ?) was an American actress. She had an affair with William Ellis Corey which led to the dissolution of his marriage, and they later married. Mabelle_Gilman_Corey ( December_4_,_1874 – ? ) was an_American_actress .
